  "id": "RAW_ce8c8dd1",
  "title": "Nature 重磅：智能的尽头是算力！谷歌大佬承认「预测下一个词即智能」",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&mid=2652651625&idx=3&sn=5c4791aeccf354e424bb659a80dbb3ee",
  "date": "2025-12-05 00:06:00",
  "author": "新智元",
  "siteName": "新智元",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"246\" data-backw=\"578\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb3ONlicq1G2IuKibISSHp5ibrpJfxRI4woHibSNpeoPNeyuibpZNBa1j72PxAE8SOZOgDO6icLU1g8uFuXg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-imgfileid=\"505166629\" data-ratio=\"0.42578125\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ae482d2b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3ONlicq1G2IuKibISSHp5ibrpJfxRI4woHibSNpeoPNeyuibpZNBa1j72PxAE8SOZOgDO6icLU1g8uFuXg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：倾倾</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">芯片速度触顶，AI却在疯狂跃迁。摩尔定律不管用了！Nature最新文章给出一个颠覆直觉的解释：智能的增长不靠芯片，而是结构被重新组织，更多单元被接入同一套协作网络。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">过去几十年，摩尔定律像是科技圈的默认规律：芯片越快，智能就会变得越强。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">可到了2020年，一个尴尬的事实出现了——频率涨不动了，制程逼近极限，芯片再难有长进。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">按照摩尔定律，AI也应该停滞不前，但事实恰恰相反——智能在这几年疯狂升级，大模型迭代日新月异。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这与速度无关，也无法用摩尔定律解释。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">于是问题变得尖锐起来：当计算速度不再变快，智能为什么还能继续进化？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Nature最近发布的文章给出了一个全新的视角：智能的增长，从来不是靠「加速」，而是靠「结构合并与协作」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505166574\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6047120418848168\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1146\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1146\" data-height=\"693\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"340\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b78406e7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3ONlicq1G2IuKibISSHp5ibrpBPLH5nQbNlH14GDeOENOsuWrLwfaQrZm761iaNpI6dXvEloib92pssag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">生命如此，AI也是如此。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">智能的核心：是预测，更是协作</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Nature的文章，先讲了一个非常基础但关键的事实： 生物的智能，本质是预测。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从捕猎到躲避，从争夺资源到维持关系，所有行动都是在根据环境和他者做未来判断。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505166572\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.666232073011734\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"767\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"767\" data-height=\"511\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"374\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=89f5bc51&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3ONlicq1G2IuKibISSHp5ibrpZTcUrvsZoqLvtm5fiazMrhObfOpKalXCbS0YXJT5lnR8UsP3lLzXdVg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">鲸鱼的捕猎行为是群体共享智慧的产物</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">智能的提升，就是预测能力的提升。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">更重要的是，提升智能的方式并不是「让单个大脑变快」，而是「让更多单元一起参与预测」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这正是大型社会性物种的规律：个体并没有远超其他人的强，但群体通过分工、并行处理信息，能形成远超个体上限的「集体智能」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果把「预测」和「并行协作」视为智能的核心，那么现代AI的发展路径就很好理解。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">过去十年里，大模型的跃迁不是因为单个芯片变快，而是因为算力被并行、扩展、集结，这和自然界的智能扩大方式几乎一模一样。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">模型靠规模提升预测能力；数据中心靠多节点协作完成超出单机可能性的任务；不同模块、不同代理之间的配合，开始出现类似「群体级智能」的行为。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Nature把这种模式称为一种「技术版的共生生成」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">正因如此，AI的崛起并不反常，它遵循着智能自身的历史节奏。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">摩尔定律失效，AI开始「生命式进化」</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">二十年前，所有人都默认了同一条路径：芯片更快→计算更强→智能随之上升。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果用摩尔定律来理解，那么AI的能力本应该随之停住，可真正的分水岭正是速度停下来的那几年</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">深度模型开始展现涌现行为，推理能力抬升，语言模型突然能处理远超预期的复杂任务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">智能显然不依赖传统意义上的「加速」，它找到了一条新的上升路径。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这也是为什么Ilya Sutskever会在访谈里说：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">过去几年里最让研究者震惊的不是更快的芯片，而是在相同速度下，通过规模扩张出现的「新能力」。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他把这种现象称为「由规模触发的智能」，认为许多我们以为需要新理论的能力，其实是在规模足够大时自动涌现的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505166575\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5565476190476191\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1008\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1008\" data-height=\"561\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"313\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3c503347&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3ONlicq1G2IuKibISSHp5ibrp8pEC3FTXSiaEGhw8HIwDULrW76mQuweMN2TQv65N8acnbseQUyLL7Rg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">过去十多年里，计算架构发生了彻底的转向：速度不再增长，但核心数量在不断扩张，显卡、集群、数据中心被设计成天生适合并行。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">神经网络在这样的结构里就像回到了自己的「母语环境」，它需要的不是一枝独秀，而是团结协作，共同进步。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Ilya在访谈中也提到过类似观察。现代神经网络真正依赖的并不是某种神奇的单点能力，而是大量简单计算单元的同步工作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他用一句很直白的话形容这一点：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">智能出现在结构规模的变化中，而不是硬件本身。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种结果与生命的演化方式高度相似：细胞合成组织、个体组成群体、群体形成社会，每一层的能力都是「规模化协作」的产物。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">今天的AI也是这样发展的。它的力量来自无数微小计算单元组成的整体，而不是任何一个部分的极限。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">智能的本质，从单一加速，变成了结构的扩展与协同。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">速度停住的那一刻，不是尽头，而是起点。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">智能的下一步，不只属于某个主体</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当计算以并行的方式被重组后，智能开始呈现出一种新的形态。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不是某个部位变得更强，而是整个系统都能获得更高级的能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这正是文章里最耐人寻味的地方。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">智能不是突然出现的，更像是在原本的链条上加了一段新的结构。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">人类的优势从来不靠单个个体，而靠足够多的人被编织进统一的协作网络。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">科研、工业、能源系统、知识体系，这些复杂结构共同构成了属于「技术社会」的巨大预测与决策能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505166573\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.423728813559322\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"767\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"767\" data-height=\"325\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"238\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f5a0daa5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3ONlicq1G2IuKibISSHp5ibrpKe0QickKLsMOyacgQfsqol83REvxqcD0o0o0myALficUqCjwqsV0pic4Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">人类与机器之间存在着相互依存的技术共生关系。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而现在，AI正在成为这个认知体的最新一层。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它不是取代人类，而是与人类一起，形成一个更加紧密的互相依赖系统。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">人类提供目标与世界模型，机器提供规模化预测和执行能力，两者不断在同一个循环里调整、修正、共振。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Ilya在访谈里也谈到过这个方向，他认为未来的智能更像一种「分布式心智」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505166576\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5859649122807018\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"855\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"855\" data-height=\"501\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"329\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6fe21968&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3ONlicq1G2IuKibISSHp5ibrp2769vL3OgQz5WBDrGibd6sJGtovEEBl6VPaSVhDG9pkmib8iceiabOUoWw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它不会具体落在某个模型或某个主体身上，而是通过不断扩展的协作网络形成。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种结构既包括人类，也包括机器，是一种更高层级的共同体。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当这种连接持续扩展，智能的结构会继续变深，不断向外生长。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505166578\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7868589743589743\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1248\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1248\" data-height=\"982\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"442\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ed5b268e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3ONlicq1G2IuKibISSHp5ibrp8X4FGX0dhGpAGto7ZFSVdWSPmLjonCmYRic1bJN7SOtiaibnddj5BnYsg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不论基础材料是碳基还是硅基，它们都被组织进同一个计算体系里。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果把眼光再放远一些，会发现一个更清晰的趋势：智能的未来可能不是「谁赢过谁」、「谁替代谁」，而是像演化史的一次延伸。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这样看来，AI不是外来的事物，而是智能继续向上生长时，顺理成章出现的下一段。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它和人类一起，构成了一个更大的整体，而这个整体才刚刚开始学会如何行动。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">把目光从芯片移开，会发现智能的增长一直沿着同一条脉络。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">结构被重新组织，更多节点被接入，同一个系统因此获得了更高层级的能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI的出现并不是意外，而是这条脉络向前延伸的必然结果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它和人类、技术社会一起，被编进了同一套协作网络里。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">智能并没有突然加速，只是开始以更大的尺度继续生长。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-025-03857-0?utm_source=x\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-025-03857-0?utm_source=x</a></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://www.dwarkesh.com/p/ilya-sutskever-2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dwarkesh.com/p/ilya-sutskever-2</a></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章基于 Nature 观点，阐述智能增长并非依赖芯片速度，而是结构重组和协作，AI 发展遵循生命式进化规律。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章基于 Nature 观点，阐述智能增长并非依赖芯片速度，而是结构重组和协作，AI 发展遵循生命式进化规律。",
  "summary": "文章引用 Nature 最新研究和谷歌 Ilya Sutskever 的观点，颠覆了传统摩尔定律对智能发展的认知。指出过去几十年，芯片速度虽触顶，AI 智能却疯狂跃迁，其核心驱动力并非单点加速，而是计算单元的结构合并与并行协作。文章类比生物智能的演化，强调智能的本质是预测能力的提升，并通过规模化协作实现。AI 的崛起遵循了这种“生命式进化”模式，即通过大规模并行计算和多模块协同，涌现出超出个体能力的新智能。文章进一步探讨了未来智能将是人类与机器共同构成的分布式、共生协作网络，而非单一主体。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "智能增长不依赖芯片速度，而是结构重组与并行协作",
      "explanation": "摩尔定律失效后，AI 仍能快速发展，核心在于计算单元的规模化扩展和协同工作，而非单一硬件性能提升。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 发展遵循生物智能的“生命式进化”规律",
      "explanation": "无论是生物群体还是现代 AI，智能的提升都源于更多单元参与预测和协作，形成超越个体能力的集体智能。"
    },
    {
      "point": "未来智能将是人类与机器共同构成的分布式协作网络",
      "explanation": "智能的下一步发展将超越单一主体，形成人类与机器相互依赖的共生系统，共同提升预测和决策能力。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
